{{Quote|The Cobral family is the largest power on Frego. They are in charge of a crime ring that has successfully controlled the government for twenty years. Rutin's father died a few years ago, of natural causes. It was widely believed that Rutin was being groomed to take over, although he has two brothers who are older than he is. Solan is the oldest and the new leader of the Cobral.|[[Jocasta Nu/Legends|Jocasta Nu]]|<ref name="Jedi Apprentice: The Only Witness">''[[Jedi Apprentice: The Only Witness]]''</ref>}}
The '''Cobral family''' was a [[The Cobral|criminal]] family that controlled the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Frego]] until [[Lena Cobral]] testified before the [[Galactic Senate/Legends|Galactic Senate]]. [[Neo-Cobral|Remnants]] of the family continued conducting criminal activities on [[Rori/Legends|Rori]] well into the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. [[Lena Cobral]] [[Marriage/Legends|married]] in to the family in [[44 BBY/Legends|44 BBY]], around the time [[Cobral father|Rutin's father]] [[Death/Legends|died]].

